Package com.whirvis.jraknet.server

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RakNetServerListener
    This interface is used by the RakNetServer to let the user know when specific events are triggered.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlockedAddress
    Represents an address that the server has blocked and stores how much time until they are unblocked.
    RakNetServer
    Used to easily create servers using the RakNet protocol.
    RakNetServerHandler
    Used by the RakNetServer with the sole purpose of sending received packets to the server so they can be handled.
    ServerPing
    Used primarily to box an identifier sent in the response of a server to a ping sent by a client so it can be modified by the user.
